parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
the transmission warning light is illuminated
grinding sounds are heard while driving
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
the vehicle jerks or hesitates when accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the drive axle can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, making it difficult or impossible to steer, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy or may deploy incorrectly.

the airbag system warning light comes on and off intermittently.

the airbag warning light is illuminated on the dashboard
the airbag system warning light comes on and off randomly.

the airbags do not deploy in the event of a crash.
